1-First go to the official website of Java SE at http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/overview/index.html

2-download JAVA SE Developement Kit 10 : ...bin.tar.gz

3-extract and move to /usr/local/jdk10

4-sudo nano /etc/profile.d/jdk10.sh
 write:

	export JAVA_HOME="/usr/local/jdk-10"
	export PATH="$PATH:${JAVA_HOME}/bin"
CTRL+X

5-reboot
